### Get shop list (page 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/shop/list?page=1&size=10

### Get shop by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/shop/1

### Get shop by name 
GET http://localhost:8080/api/shop/of/name?name=测试商铺1&current=1&size=10

### Get shop by type (typeId=1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/shop/of/type?typeId=1&current=1&size=10


